up leaders click submit step 2 the incoming president or financial officer must log into mygroups select your group affiliation if needed complete the registration form once all required fields are complete click on submit application follow up with others listed on the application to have them log in and sign the application step 3 the listed members of the group must log into mygroups select your group affiliation if needed review the listed information click sign application back to top changing leadership mid year if one of your group leaders changes mid year you may simply make an edit to your current mygroups registration edits can be made by either the president or financial officer to make your edit log into mygroups select your group affiliation if needed click edit to the bottom left of the basic section replace the old leader's sunet user names with the new leader's sunet user names click update click send sig emails to remind the new leaders to sign the registration form if you are doing your annual transition ie changing most or all of your group leadership we suggest you create a new registration following the process for annual re registration back to top overcoming registration problems i think my group should be finished with registration but is still not approved go to your group's online form in mygroups and scroll down to the signatures sections you can check to see if everyone in your group has signed off electronically if someone hasn t scroll to the top of the form and click send sig emails this will send an email link to all those that still need to sign for your group if everything looks like it is done email your sal advisor listed on the top left hand section of the online form and ask them to approve your group i can t access mygroups to sign the form it's likely that someone entered your sunet user name incorrectly oftentimes people accidentally enter your email address or student id number instead of your username contact sal to have your username corrected it's also possible that last year's group leaders haven t created a registration form for this year contact your group's leaders to remind them to create the registration form if they ve left campus contact sal back to top mygroups vs mygroups2 up banking funding groups sal printer friendly version calendar connect with sal facebook sal on facebook stanfordsal stanfordsal sal quick links about sal student organizations directory workshop schedule find a venue ordering equipment & services mygroups registration funding sources tsf partnership program mygroups2 space requests find a policy white plaza information 5 sure security escorts starting a new group copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
